<L>__{interior new york city office building. day.}
<A>__{a very beautiful young woman in a business suit, in an elevator. the doors open and scott, dressed in a suit, gets in. he turns to face the front. they ride up in silence. the doors open on a mezzanine. there are several men at the end of the mezzanine. scott starts to get out, and the girl tries to stop him. he shoves her roughly back into the elevator. several of the men come toward scott, and a large, portly businessman in his forties (avi) calls them off. scott comes forward.}
